reviewText: this dvd is kind of lame since it's just rivers singing while alot of amatuer people are playing the music.

Amazing DVD..

Loving how Rivers did the spontaneous setlist for the gig.
Very humble and intimate show.

Good job Rivers :)

This DVD is a medley of songs, new and old, from both Weezer's and Rivers Cuomo's solo albums. Performed by Rivers himself plus a collection of amateur musicians, a wide spectrum of musical talent and fan dedication is shown as they preform hit after hit. The extras include awesome behind the scene recordings of Cuomo's Alone II, interviews, and videos. This disc is a must have for any Weezer or Rivers fan!
